{"tid":734590,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵番一隻舊既PC對戰射擊Game","createTime":"2018-07-08T18:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T18:15:41.000Z","uid":13301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5523ac44604d588de5a15b2c1aa3bce2b54a4d39","tid":734590,"uid":13301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"隻Game差唔多十幾年前出 第一身射擊game黎既<br />\n係PC既<br />\n細個睇阿哥玩 係分紅藍兩隊<br />\n一開始spawn係個屋企好似battlefield咁有車可以拎黎揸 但係就未來feel好多 有laser又盛<br />\n兩team個基地有座主堡 開波初期行近去個主堡會比個主堡秒殺<br />\n可以裝炸彈裝C4炸人到炸人地基地既建築物<br />\n想問全能既連登仔會唔會知隻game叫咩名<br />\n細個阿哥比我玩我唔識玩<br />\n大個左想搵番呢隻game出黎 懷念一下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d04e266521b5490daabfdb16be8fc106e7cbc1","tid":734590,"uid":13301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:01:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7630880ad59e367067d19eecab0e538c68ea0e07","tid":734590,"uid":13301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:01:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2c04784d17a8028c37aeae7ccca81e5c540af762","tid":734590,"uid":132660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:08:31.000Z","msg":"Battlefield 2142?"},{"pid":"2ef0847c1fd1c0c3001e093d5657e7ece1064e47","tid":734590,"uid":75020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:09:33.000Z","msg":"MKZ ?"},{"pid":"66718300441b2fbfca0082605b2301bdabb51dfb","tid":734590,"uid":35388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/021320_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-th